type

private int type
Type of the affected resource: XML_INCIDENCE, ASSET_INCIDENCE

affectedArea

private int affectedArea
Affected area (sub-type). For XML: ASSESSMENT_INCIDENCE, ADAPTATION_INCIDENCE, CHAPTER_INCIDENCE, DESCRIPTOR_INCIDENCE For Asset: Category of the asset (see AssetsController)

affectedResource

private String affectedResource
Path of the affected File

importance

private int importance
Importance of the incidence. Low-important incidences will not affect directly the game. Medium-important incidences will vary slightly the behaviour of the game, but not significantly. High important incidences will make some parts of the games unplayable and Critical ones will make them completely unreadable.

message

private String message
String containing a message which describes the problem found reading the damaged file

referenced

private boolean referenced
Indicates if the damaged file was referenced inside the XML or just was contained in the zip / folder
